汤。”<br><br>“如果你爸听到你这么说一定会很高兴的。”聂小素低着头说。<br><br>“我可以帮你什么吗？”<br><br>聂小素把处理好的鸡切成了小块，然后放到了烧开的高压锅中，她檫了檫额头的汗水说：“不用了这里我来就行了。”<br><br>“那我去摆放好餐桌。”赵俞昊带着一些碗筷离开了厨房，几分钟后高压锅的壶嘴上冒起了气泡，聂小素听着餐厅叮叮咚咚的声音不禁问：“你摆好了吗？”<br><br>“还没……没那么快。”赵俞昊飞快的说，“现在几点了。”<br><br>“奇怪，手表不在你自己手上吗？”聂小素不解的问。<br><br>赵俞昊好象突然醒悟过来，他看了看手表哈哈大笑的说：“看来爸就要来了。”\u0018","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 08:22","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":29,"title":"回复：【文文】鸡毛","content":"应该每超出50字吧","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9edf9a0a.rfXLTL3kf8i5QNypvTEXuw&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 08:23","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/forum/pic/item/a1b5a86efa54aad181cb4a98.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":30,"title":"回复：【文文】鸡毛","content":"...= =&nbsp;&nbsp;  没必要  长篇看起来更爽...  【PS 回帖的速度会降低...】","author":"ㄗs崩潰","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec9ccd24.cuLXh91xYg_HgiUkfkPLhg&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 08:27","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/timelees1125/mpic/item/24e0f4ef96270b0b2cf53474.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":31,"title":"回复：【文文】鸡毛","content":"FY...？","author":"ㄗs崩潰","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec9ccd24.cuLXh91xYg_HgiUkfkPLhg&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 08:28","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/%D6%ED%D6%EDde%D0%A1%CE%DD/mpic/item/28c2017f8cb83d2a28388aaa.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":32,"title":"回复：回复：【文文】鸡毛","content":"万岁...~  》《&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  【于是我看到了验证码...】","author":"ㄗs崩潰","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec9ccd24.cuLXh91xYg_HgiUkfkPLhg&fr=pb","date":"2009-07-18 08:28","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":"https://imgsa.baidu.com/timelees1125/mpic/item/24e0f4ef96270b0b2cf53474.jpg?v=tbs"},{"index":33,"title":"回复：回复：【文文】鸡毛","content":"回复：30楼<br>可是要满足遗失の梦幻的要求啊！","author":"幻灭之尘","author_link":"https://tieba.b